#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: cc-utf8-converter.php
msgid "CC UTF8 Converter"
msgstr "CC UTF8 轉換器"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#. Author URI of the plugin
#: cc-utf8-converter.php
msgid "https://cclin.cc"
msgstr "https://cclin.cc"

#. Description of the plugin
#: cc-utf8-converter.php
msgid ""
"Convert uploaded plain text files (BIG5, SJIS, GB2312, etc.) to UTF-8 and "
"download them automatically. Supports both admin and frontend, and temporary "
"files are deleted after download."
msgstr ""
"將上傳的純文字檔案（BIG5、SJIS、GB2312 等）轉換為 UTF-8 並自動下載。支援前台與後台使用，下載後暫存檔案會自動刪除。"

#. Author of the plugin
#: cc-utf8-converter.php
msgid "Chance Lin"
msgstr "Chance Lin"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:51 cc-utf8-converter.php:52
msgid "UTF-8 Converter"
msgstr "UTF-8 轉換器"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:69
msgid "File to UTF-8"
msgstr "檔案轉換為 UTF-8"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:71
msgid "Convert any text file encoding to Unicode UTF-8."
msgstr "將任何文字檔案編碼轉換為 Unicode UTF-8。"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:75
msgid "Choose a file to convert"
msgstr "選擇要轉換的檔案"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:88
msgid "Drag a file here, or click to choose a file."
msgstr "拖曳檔案到這裡，或點擊選擇檔案"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:91 cc-utf8-converter.php:131
msgid "No file selected."
msgstr "尚未選擇任何檔案"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:95
msgid "Supported formats: .txt, .htm, .html, .xhtml, .csv, .xml, .md"
msgstr "支援格式：.txt、.htm、.html、.xhtml、.csv、.xml、.md"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:104
msgid "Convert to UTF-8 and Download"
msgstr "轉換為 UTF-8 並下載"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:106
msgid "Help"
msgstr "說明"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:113
msgid ""
"Traditional Chinese text files were often encoded in Big5 in the past. If "
"old files are not converted to UTF-8 first, they may display garbled text in "
"different editors, systems, or browsers. This tool converts text files "
"directly to UTF-8 without opening the original file."
msgstr ""
"早期繁體中文文字檔多使用 Big5 編碼。若未先轉換為 UTF-8，在不同編輯器、系統或瀏覽器中可能出現亂碼。此工具可在不開啟原始檔案的情況下，直接將文字檔轉換為 UTF-8。"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:116
msgid ""
"1. Automatically detects common encodings such as UTF-8, BIG5, SJIS, and "
"GB2312."
msgstr "1. 自動判斷常見編碼，例如 UTF-8、BIG5、SJIS、GB2312。"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:117
msgid "2. Converts file content to UTF-8."
msgstr "2. 將檔案內容轉換為 UTF-8。"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:118
msgid "3. Replaces unsupported or invalid characters with ■."
msgstr "3. 將不支援或無效字元以 ■ 取代。"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:119
msgid ""
"4. Downloads the converted file directly and does not keep it on the server."
msgstr "4. 轉換完成後直接下載，伺服器不保留檔案。"

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:132
msgid "Selected: "
msgstr "已選擇："

#: cc-utf8-converter.php:257
msgid "Upload error."
msgstr "上傳錯誤"